Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:40.78,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Oh man...\N{\rHamada} - That's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:42.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's my plan\N{\rEndo} - I get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:46.99,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It'd be bad if I don't have anything to read, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:51.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Come on guys, what's this? A prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:54.16,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Oh boy...
