Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:21.32,Black,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\fade(250,750)\pos(714.6,902)}From Matsumoto to Hosei:{\rYellow\fs70} a letter of gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's Matsumoto's letter for his beloved junior
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Dear Yamazaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:38.44,Reading,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I never thought I'd be writing you a letter{\alphaHFF\t(4500,495,\alpha100)}\N\N\N\N\N\Nin my entire life, let alone a letter of gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:45.35,Reading,,0,0,0,,If there's something I should be grateful to you for,{\alphaHFF\t(4400,1,\alpha100)}\N\N\N\N\N\Nit's from the time Downtown had success in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:52.42,Reading,,0,0,0,,And I was at the peak of my popularity,{\alphaHFF\t(4000,495,\alpha100)}\N\N\N\N\N\Nbeing featured in over 10 regular shows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:57.59,Reading,,0,0,0,,But no one ever asked for my opinion,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(3100,495,\alpha100)} I was nothing more than a yes-man
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:08.54,Reading,,0,0,0,,But only you, between all of them,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(6100,495,\alpha100)}you told me, "are you an idiot, Matsumoto?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:17.55,Reading,,0,0,0,,You got near me with your usual friendly smile{\alphaHFF\t(5100,495,\alpha100)}\N\N\N\N\N\Nand told me lots of funny stories everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:32.93,Reading,,0,0,0,,When I looked at you, always behaving like that,{\alphaHFF\t(5000,495,\alpha100)}\N\N\N\N\N\N I thought {\alphaHFF\t(8100,495,\alpha100)}"It would be nice to have a little brother like him"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:38.80,Reading,,0,0,0,,I always thought of you as my little brother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:39.64,Reading,,0,0,0,,One more thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:43.81,Reading,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if this is a thank you or an apology,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:49.01,Reading,,0,0,0,,But five years ago, when we were walking down Roppongi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:04:00.42,Reading,,0,0,0,,We got attacked {\alphaHFF\t(2800,495,\alpha100)}by 5-6 gangsters, do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:06.60,Reading,,0,0,0,,I was trembling with fear, my legs were shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:10.47,Reading,,0,0,0,,But you suddenly jumped towards them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:14.17,Reading,,0,0,0,,And you shielded me, saying "run away, Matsumoto!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:19.44,Reading,,0,0,0,,Sorry for running away, that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.28,Reading,,0,0,0,,But then you came to my house
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:28.08,Reading,,0,0,0,,You told me "it's alright", with your face all swollen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:33.96,Reading,,0,0,0,,And then you showed me again that friendly smile of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:41.83,Reading,,0,0,0,,From that day on, I decided I needed to protect you,{\alphaHFF\t(3500,495,\alpha100)}\N\N\N\N\N\N and not the other way round, so I started working out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:52.48,Reading,,0,0,0,,And now I'm friends with all the musclehead comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.35,Reading,,0,0,0,,If you didn't show me your courage, that day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:05:01.08,Reading,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'd be a muscle-comedian to this day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.75,Reading,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much, Yamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:06.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:11.83,Reading,,0,0,0,,You chose to become a rakugoka, a wonderful job
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:18.07,Reading,,0,0,0,,You study so much and work really hard,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(3200,1,\alpha100}I'm sure you'll become a master in no time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:23.37,Reading,,0,0,0,,And when that happens,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(2500,1,\alpha100}let me, your biggest fan, hear a rakugo story
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:31.18,Reading,,0,0,0,,And when I'll eventually stop being a comedian,{\alphaHFF\t(3400,495,\alpha100)}\N\N\N\N\N\Nplease stay with me {\alphaHFF\t(5500,495,\alpha100)}as my brother
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:40.62,Reading,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}To my little brother, {\alphaHFF\t(4500,495,\alpha100)}Tsukitei Hosei
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:40.62,Reading,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(724,947.333)}Signed: Matsumoto Hitoshi, from Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:45.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I see...\N{\rEndo} - I didn't know about that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:48.40,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's news to me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:49.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,I didn't know it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:52.80,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You really remember a lot of stuff, don't you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:56.61,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Your memories are really good
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:06:00.41,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I have lots of things I've forgotten myself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.41,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,931.333)}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:01.11,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:05.01,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I may have forgotten about them, but you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.55,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Just how many things do you remember?
