Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:26.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,What the hell is happening, today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.43,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Here\N{\rManabe} - Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.43,Hosei,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on, staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:31.53,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect this guest, to be honest
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,926)}I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:35.58,Manabe,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,866)}- Can I drink it? Cheers, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.58,Hosei,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm gonna scold the staff, later
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.98,Manabe,,0,0,0,,Cheers!\N{\rHosei} - Alright, alright, cheers I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.81,Endo,,0,0,0,,Manabe's image doesn't really line up with Hosei's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.98,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad she's here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:50.25,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I mean, this bar was getting pretty melancholic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.12,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(721.2,921.6)}I agree{\rManabe}   - Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:54.59,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(721.2,921.6)}Now she can liven up the mood a bit, I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.62,Manabe,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm glad
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.30,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.46,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's more lively now\N{\rManabe} - I'm glad, guys
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:00.56,Manabe,,0,0,0,,After all today's... you know, Hosei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:03.13,Manabe,,0,0,0,,It's your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.13,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,926)}That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:06.27,Manabe,,0,0,0,,It's his birthday\N{\rHamada} - Wow, she actually knows that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.77,Manabe,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to come here today
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:15.45,Manabe,,0,0,0,,And since you're having this set up for today, I wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:21.05,Manabe,,0,0,0,,I wanted to let Hosei know about some things...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.05,Hosei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,926)}Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.39,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You meant that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.74,Manabe,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,926)}Yeah, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:27.12,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You came here for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.73,Manabe,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.46,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You tricked me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.56,Manabe,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a good moment, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:35.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Did you write a letter?\N{\rManabe} - I did, actually
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.00,Manabe,,0,0,0,,So, can I read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.57,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I mean, she's here already, just listen to her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.57,Hosei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,926)}Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.92,Manabe,,0,0,0,,{\pos(708,851.6)}- Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.14,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Alright, but please, read it cheerfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.14,Manabe,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,926)}Alright, in a positive way!\N{\rHosei} - Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:49.15,Hosei,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere got really tense in here, enough of that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.50,Manabe,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,926)}I see
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.15,Manabe,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,926)}Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.95,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So read it cheerfully ok? Go!\N{\rManabe} - Sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.38,Manabe,,0,0,0,,Dear Hosei,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:09:01.76,Reading,,0,0,0,,We happen to meet frequently when we're working,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:06.50,Reading,,0,0,0,,And I bet you think all we do is just say hi to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:10.97,Reading,,0,0,0,,But it's not the same for me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:21.74,Reading,,0,0,0,,To be honest, {\alphaHFF\t(1600,495,\alpha100)}before I entered the showbiz,\N\N\N\N\N\N {\alphaHFF\t(4200,495,\alpha100)}I used to be {\alphaHFF\t(6700,495,\alpha100)}your biggest groupie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:25.55,Reading,,0,0,0,,My youth was painted in your colors, Hosei
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:33.36,Reading,,0,0,0,,As soon as I finished school,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(2800,1,\alpha1} I rushed my way towards the TV stations to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:38.76,Reading,,0,0,0,,And I always checked every show\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(2000,1,\alpha100} you could have popped up in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:45.40,Reading,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,944)}I especially liked "Kurobuta Tengoku" from Tokyo TV
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:45.40,Reading,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(751.2,880)}Black Pig Paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:50.94,Reading,,0,0,0,,And of course, I still have lots of Hosei-themed goods\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(1900,1,\alpha100} in my parents' house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:54.28,Reading,,0,0,0,,Tee-hee! How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:10:02.45,Reading,,0,0,0,,Before entering college, I was scouted\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(3600,1,\alpha100}by someone from the showbiz in Shibuya's Yoshinoya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:07.39,Reading,,0,0,0,,And the first thing I thought was "I get to enter Hosei's world!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:17.83,Reading,,0,0,0,,And the first time I met Hosei in real life,{\alphaHFF\t(4300,495,\alpha100)}\N\N\N\N\N\NI was so nervous all I could do {\alphaHFF\t(6900,495,\alpha100)}was watching you from a distance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:24.47,Reading,,0,0,0,,That time you glanced over at me only once,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(3200,495,\alpha100)} and that's my most treasured memory
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.91,Reading,,0,0,0,,Tee-hee! I actually said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:32.85,Reading,,0,0,0,,From that moment on, we even shared some TV shows together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:39.26,Reading,,0,0,0,,But my girly heart was so nervous,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(3000,1,\alpha100} I couldn't talk to you at all
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:46.26,Reading,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, this was supposed to be a gratitude letter,\N\N\N\N\N\N {\alphaHFF\t(3600,1,\alpha100)}but it ended up being a sort of love letter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:49.93,Reading,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, {\alphaHFF\t(1600,495,\alpha100)}tee-hee
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:49.93,Reading,,0,0,0,,{\p1\blur1\fscx130\fscy200\pos(922,1078)}m 0 -4 l 1 -6 l 3 -7 l 5 -7 l 6 -7 l 7 -7 l 8 -6 l 9 -5 l 10 -3 l 10 -1 l 9 2 l 7 5 l 2 9 l 0 11 l -7 5 l -9 2 l -10 0 l -10 -2 l -10 -4 l -9 -6 l -7 -7 l -5 -7 l -3 -7 l -2 -6 l -1 -5
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:56.77,Reading,,0,0,0,,There are lots of reasons for why I'm grateful to you,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(4100,495,\alpha100)}but if I have to say one in particular
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:11:02.28,Reading,,0,0,0,,That would be the third time I met you while we were working
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:05.31,Reading,,0,0,0,,That day, you were kind of different...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:12.52,Reading,,0,0,0,,I remember seeing you in a corner, looking cool,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(2600,495,\alpha100)} typing a draft on your PC by yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.76,Reading,,0,0,0,,When I looked at you like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:23.20,Reading,,0,0,0,,I thought "that's right, maybe Hosei can get to know me\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(2300,1,\alpha100} if it's through a PC!" {\alphaHFF\t(4700,495,\alpha100)}and so I started my own blog
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:30.64,Reading,,0,0,0,,I always waited for the day Hosei would notice me,{\alphaHFF\t(3950,100,\alpha100)} \N\N\N\N\N\Nand I kept updating my blog on a daily basis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:35.58,Reading,,0,0,0,,And then, one day, the media started\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(2400,1,\alpha100} referring to me as "the Blog Queen",
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:40.58,Reading,,0,0,0,,And I was able to get lots of job offers from that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:49.23,Reading,,0,0,0,,That blog I've created just to be seen by you\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(3000,495,\alpha100)} changed my entire life forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:56.87,Reading,,0,0,0,,Maybe it makes sense only inside my head,\N\N\N\N\N\N {\alphaHFF\t(3200,495,\alpha100)}but I'm really grateful for what you've done
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:02.84,Reading,,0,0,0,,You chose to become a rakugoka, a wonderful job
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:06.24,Reading,,0,0,0,,I don't think you know this, but actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:05.51,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&HCCC&}Rakugo? Again?\N{\rEndo\alpha&HCCC&}- Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:16.19,Reading,,0,0,0,,Truth be told, {\alphaHFF\t(3200,495,\alpha100)}I snuck up several times to see you perform\N\N\N\N\N\N your rakugo skits, {\alphaHFF\t(7050,495,\alpha100)}and sometimes I waited for you outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:25.29,Reading,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)}Hosei,{\alphaHFF\t(1800,495,\alpha100)} thank you for {\alphaHFF\t(3750,495,\alpha100)}making me experience such youth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:25.29,Reading,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(724,947.333)}Signed: Manabe Kaori
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:32.10,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I see...\N{\rHosei} - Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.34,Endo,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that's the story behind her blog
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:39.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There's a lot we can't know, if we don't ask
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:39.81,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,926)}That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.61,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I had no idea, really
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.02,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:48.48,Manabe,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,923.333)}You really saved me, I owe you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:51.92,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You've been so good at hiding it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.29,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You were my groupie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.29,Manabe,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,923.333)}That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:13:00.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Since I was part of TEAM-0?{Hosei's former comedy duo}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.50,Manabe,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,923.333)}Yes, that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.38,Hosei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,923.333)}Since TEAM-0?!\N{\rManabe}- Since TEAM-0
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,923.333)}But really, mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:03.77,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Let's call it a day, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:09.61,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm running out of tears here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:10.77,Manabe,,0,0,0,,- Can I have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:13.06,Manabe,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,More?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.25,Manabe,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,More?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,0)\shad0\3c&HB260E5&\pos(721.8,911.333)}Shimoda Kageki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.89,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Seriously...\N{\rShimoda} - You were here, huh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:29.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hi there, Shimoda
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:32.16,Shimoda,,0,0,0,,It's been a while\N{\rMatsumoto} - Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.66,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So what do you...\N{\rHosei} - You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.87,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What do you want to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.87,Shimoda,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,923.333)}- Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:40.47,Shimoda,,0,0,0,,Sweet potato shochu, mixed with hot water
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:42.87,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Sweet potato shochu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:45.47,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Sweet potato shochu, huh?\N{\rShimoda} - With hot water, please
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.31,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's a pro at writing, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.68,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's right, he's a professional
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.78,Shimoda,,0,0,0,,Cheers\N{\rMatsumoto} - Nice atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:52.95,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Here's to you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:57.59,Shimoda,,0,0,0,,Cheers, cheers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:01.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is a surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Really? \N{\rHosei} - What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:06.56,Shimoda,,0,0,0,,Can I read you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.56,Hosei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,923.333)}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:09.33,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Whatever, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:12.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I have no idea about his relation with Yama-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:14.55,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,923.333)}I didn't know they knew each other\N{\rHamada} - That's news to me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.51,Shimoda,,0,0,0,,To my dear Hosei-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:32.26,Reading,,0,0,0,,Hosei-chan, {\alphaHFF\t(2000,495,\alpha100)}it's been {\alphaHFF\t(3780,495,\alpha100)}almost 3 years since we last met,\N\N\N\N\N\N {\alphaHFF\t(8300,495,\alpha100)}how have you been doing since?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:36.39,Reading,,0,0,0,,Today I'm here to tell you how grateful I am to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:42.00,Reading,,0,0,0,,But I want to start by recalling our memories together
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:47.10,Reading,,0,0,0,,Me and Hosei-chan first met around 20 years ago{hey, I subbed this clip!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:52.44,Reading,,0,0,0,,We had this episode in which\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(2300,1,\alpha100} I appeared inside your fantasy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:15:00.58,Reading,,0,0,0,,And we slapped each other,{\alphaHFF\t(2300,495,\alpha100)}\N\N\N\N\N\N and in the end, we kissed.{\alphaHFF\t(6200,495,\alpha100)} That was it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:06.82,Reading,,0,0,0,,That time, {\alphaHFF\t(3050,495,\alpha100)}we parted our ways without getting any closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:13.80,Reading,,0,0,0,,But we had a miraculous second encounter\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(4300,495,\alpha100)} at the hair salon we both went to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:17.67,Reading,,0,0,0,,And then, Hosei-chan, you suddenly told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:26.94,Reading,,0,0,0,,"I happen to know{\alphaHFF\t(1900,495,\alpha100)} a clothing store which I think\N\N\N\N\N\Nis perfect for your tastes,{\alphaHFF\t(5700,495,\alpha100)} wanna go there with me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:30.85,Reading,,0,0,0,,And so we went shopping together
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:38.39,Reading,,0,0,0,,It was a shop in Nippori full of fancy stuff,\N\N\N\N\N\N {\alphaHFF\t(3200,495,\alpha100)}some of those clothes were a bit showy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:49.00,Reading,,0,0,0,,And there,{\alphaHFF\t(2300,495,\alpha100)} you bought me fishnet stockings,\N\N\N\N\N\N {\alphaHFF\t(4900,495,\alpha100)}which were perfect for my tastes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:58.41,Reading,,0,0,0,,From that day on{\alphaHFF\t(2850,495,\alpha100)} everything else happened so naturally,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(5900,495,\alpha100)} and in the end, we started living together
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:08.15,Reading,,0,0,0,,The life I shared with you was really exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:16.66,Reading,,0,0,0,,You were particularly picky on my fashion sense,\N\N\N\N\N\N {\alphaHFF\t(3620,495,\alpha100)}you told me "no-sleeves is too flashy, don't wear it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:22.77,Reading,,0,0,0,,You gave me lots of advice,\N\N\N\N\N\N{\alphaHFF\t(3000,495,\alpha100)} such as wearing more than 10 colors together
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:29.27,Reading,,0,0,0,,And after 17 years of living together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:36.61,Reading,,0,0,0,,A period marking the end of our life together finally came
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:44.95,Reading,,0,0,0,,You became a rakugoka, and moved away to Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:49.09,Reading,,0,0,0,,The day before you left our house,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:53.23,Reading,,0,0,0,,We went to the hot springs together
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.53,Reading,,0,0,0,,And then we talked all night about silly stories at the Bamiyan{chain of chinese restaurants}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:17:01.27,Reading,,0,0,0,,Like that time we went to pick up girls in Odaiba
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:08.74,Reading,,0,0,0,,We recalled so many things, {\alphaHFF\t(2850,495,\alpha100)}and we cried together, {\alphaHFF\t(4600,495,\alpha100)}until dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:21.46,Reading,,0,0,0,,Hosei-chan, {\alphaHFF\t(2500,495,\alpha100)}you're the one{\alphaHFF\t(4500,495,\alpha100)} who brought the most joy\N\N\N\N\N\N in my life, {\alphaHFF\t(6700,495,\alpha100)}the life of an old 74 years old man
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:26.90,Reading,,0,0,0,,And I'm {\alphaHFF\t(3200,495,\alpha100)}truly grateful for that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:32.37,Reading,,0,0,0,,And now you chose to become a rakugoka, a wonderful job
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:42.91,Reading,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)}I still dream of the day {\alphaHFF\t(5800,495,\alpha100)}we can live together again
