Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an4\bord0\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(431,151.333)}1 room (8 tatami)\N- Bathtub\N - TV\N- Front door\N- Kitchen\N\Nin Kugayama
